APP DISCLAIMER

Unity Texture Generator is a local development and editor application for creating, editing, combining and exporting textures, layers, materials, simple animations, helper data, generated assets and project-related working contexts. The application can generate previews, files, exports, suggestions, AI-assisted outputs and textual or visual helper data, but it does not replace independent professional, legal, security, licensing, compatibility or production review.

All generated content, exported files, AI-assisted results, materials, textures, configuration data and project outputs must be checked by the user before use, publication, distribution, execution or integration into other projects. The application is provided as development software and may contain incomplete features, development defaults, platform-dependent behavior, local runtime artifacts and optional third-party dependencies.

External links, including repository, GitHub, PayPal, donation, documentation or support links, may open in the browser. Donations are voluntary, go exclusively to Eric Heidrich / Nrwx, do not unlock additional rights, features or permissions, and are not required for using the application.

